OL,3,CBoy hails new-found 'freedom' after
OL,4,C#1.6m treatment
OL,6,FThe treatment works by editing the
OL,7,Ffaulty gene in a patient's own stem
OL,8,Fcells.
OL,10,FAdam, 13, was one of the first
OL,11,Fchildren to receive the treatment,
OL,12,Faccording to NHS Blood and Transplant
OL,13,F(NHSBT).
OL,15,FHe said: "It is nice to have my
OL,16,Ffreedom back and not be in hospital
OL,17,Fanymore."
