OL,3,CBoy hails new-found 'freedom' after
OL,4,C#1.6m treatment
OL,6,FAdam was born with beta-thalassaemia,
OL,7,Fan inherited blood disorder that means
OL,8,Fthe haemoglobin in the blood does not
OL,9,Fwork properly, affecting how oxygen is
OL,10,Fcarried around the body.
OL,12,FSymptoms include anaemia and chronic
OL,13,Fpain, and in severe cases the
OL,14,Fcondition can be life threatening.
OL,16,FSince he was eight months old, Adam
OL,17,Frelied on monthly blood transfusions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
