OL,3,CBoy hails new-found 'freedom' after
OL,4,C#1.6m treatment
OL,6,FHis older sister, who had the same
OL,7,Fcondition, was given a stem cell
OL,8,Ftransplant in 2023 but no stem cell
OL,9,Fmatch could be found for Adam.
OL,11,FIn November 2024, when he was 12, Adam
OL,12,Freceived the specialist treatment,
OL,13,Fwhich involves his stem cells being
OL,14,Fcollected and taken to a laboratory
OL,15,Fwhere the Crispr technology is used.
OL,17,FThe edited cells are then infused
OL,18,Fback, which prompts the body to
OL,19,Fproduce healthy red blood cells.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
