OL,3,CBoy hails new-found 'freedom' after
OL,4,C#1.6m treatment
OL,6,FCasgevy is an option for patients when
OL,7,Fa stem cell transplant is suitable but
OL,8,Fno donor can be found.
OL,10,FA confidential deal has been struck
OL,11,Fbetween the NHS and manufacturer
OL,12,FVertex, which means it is likely to be
OL,13,Fpaying less than the official price of
OL,14,F#1.65 million per patient.
OL,16,FNow Adam has reunited with the nurse
OL,17,Fthat cared for him during treatment `
OL,18,FNHSBT therapeutic apheresis specialist
OL,19,Fnurse Clair Baron.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
