OL,3,CBoy hails new-found 'freedom' after
OL,4,C#1.6m treatment
OL,6,FAdam said, "It feels nice to be back
OL,7,Fhere because I can see the nurses who
OL,8,Ftreated me in the past.
OL,10,F"It's really good to see Clair and to
OL,11,Fbe able to say thank you to her ` she
OL,12,Fwas the start of my treatment and now
OL,13,FI'm much better.
OL,15,F"But it is nice to have my freedom
OL,16,Fback and not be in hospital anymore."
