OL,3,CBoy hails new-found 'freedom' after
OL,4,C#1.6m treatment
OL,6,FAdam's father, Anzaq Rehman, 43,
OL,7,Fadded: "It feels great to be back here
OL,8,Fand to be reunited with Clair ` we're
OL,9,Fso grateful for the role that she
OL,10,Fplayed in Adam's journey, she was that
OL,11,Ffirst step towards where we are now
OL,12,Fand that's so special."
OL,14,FMs Baron said: "It's absolutely
OL,15,Fwonderful to see Adam, it genuinely
OL,16,Fis, seeing how well he is doing is
OL,17,Fjust brilliant.
