OL,3,CBoy hails new-found 'freedom' after
OL,4,C#1.6m treatment
OL,6,F"To see him now, out on the other
OL,7,Fside, back at school and being able to
OL,8,Fenjoy activities in a way he couldn't
OL,9,Fbefore, is just incredible.
OL,11,F"The gene therapy has given him his
OL,12,Flife back and it's an honour to be a
OL,13,Fpart of his story."
OL,15,FTeresa Baines, head of therapeutic
OL,16,Fapheresis services (TAS) at NHS Blood
OL,17,Fand Transplant, said: "It's incredible
OL,18,Fto see Adam doing so well in such a
OL,19,Fshort amount of time. Gene therapies
OL,20,Fare truly life-changing treatments.
